WEBVTT


00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:02.360
Integrity means thing on us

00:00:02.360 --> 00:00:05.020
and having strong moral principles.

00:00:05.080 --> 00:00:08.740
A person with integrity we have ethically

00:00:08.840 --> 00:00:10.160
and that's the right thing.

00:00:10.160 --> 00:00:11.860
Even behind closed doors,

00:00:12.440 --> 00:00:13.500
you may ask

00:00:13.680 --> 00:00:16.300
how do we demonstrate integrity at work?

00:00:16.800 --> 00:00:19.540
There are some simple ways to start.

00:00:19.840 --> 00:00:22.000
Respecting the privacy of colleagues

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:23.860
in private conversations,

00:00:24.200 --> 00:00:26.100
communicating honestly,

00:00:27.040 --> 00:00:29.980
taking responsibility for your actions,

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:32.100
making promises to keep

00:00:32.200 --> 00:00:34.680
supporting your organizations value

00:00:34.680 --> 00:00:36.660
with or without recognition,

00:00:37.040 --> 00:00:38.680
acknowledging your colleagues

00:00:38.680 --> 00:00:40.940
when they perform high quality work

00:00:41.800 --> 00:00:45.340
and being trustworthy. After all,

00:00:45.640 --> 00:00:48.900
employee who can demonstrate integrity in the workplace

00:00:49.200 --> 00:00:51.620
enjoy great working relationships

00:00:51.640 --> 00:00:54.980
with supportive and light minded colleagues.

00:00:55.320 --> 00:00:57.840
You will be more likely to earn promotions

00:00:57.840 --> 00:01:01.600
and enjoy the satisfaction of being a valid team member

00:01:01.600 --> 00:01:05.780
too. That's all we want to share about integrity at work.

00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:09.940
We wish you all the best in your working life. Thank you.
